<h1>Masters Thesis Seminar</h1>

<h2>January - April '14</h2>

<p>This seminar will be devoted to a discussion of the work currently being carried out by its participants. That means this whole seminar is an elaborate excuse for me to bully my friends into talking about the stuff they've been reading. You should, however, be warned: the talks may, at this point, not have anything at all to do with the speaker's masters theses.</p>

<p>We meet every Saturday at 10:30 am in Hall 123.</p>

